p: \rThis lighthouse is more of a tower than anything else.
\rThere're no lights and only a few really small windows at the top!
\bOur Gym Leader, Diana, was chosen by a legendary Pokemon when she was young.
\bThat's probably why she's so strong today!
\bWe used to have a Dark-type Gym in Torren, but it was disbanded when the First Augur disappeared.
\bThat's right! The First Augur was a Dark-type Gym Leader!
\bHe's the only one in the whole wide world!
